/*  XR FRAME — CORRECTED MATH
    pose.transform.matrix is column-major viewer-to-world.
    Cols: [0-3]=X(right), [4-7]=Y(up), [8-11]=Z(backward)
    YAW:   atan2(pm[8], pm[10]) — Z-col x,z. 0 at rest, +CW right.
    PITCH: asin(-pm[9]) — forward.y = -Z_y = -pm[9]. Positive up.
    ROLL:  atan2(-pm[4], pm[5]) — Y-col tilt. Positive = right tilt. */
